1)CLUSTER IP

CLUSTERIP: It will work inside the cluster.
it will not expose to outer world.

apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: suii
  labels:
    app: phonepay
spec:
  containers:
    - name: cont1
      image: saivardhan53/airepo:latest
      ports:
        - containerPort: 80

===========================================
2)NodePort

NODEPORT: It will expose our application in a particular port.
Range: 30000 - 32767 (in sg we need to give all traffic)

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  labels:
    app: swiggy
  name: swiggy-deploy
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: swiggy
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: swiggy
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: cont1
        image: rahamshaik/trainservice:latest
        ports:
          - containerPort: 80


==============================================================
3.LOAD BALANCER
LOADBALACER: It will expose our app and distribute load blw pods.

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  labels:
    app: swiggy
  name: swiggy-deploy
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: swiggy
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: swiggy
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: cont1
        image: rahamshaik/trainservice:latest
        ports:
          - containerPort: 80
